README

Simplocation

Simplification of Data visualisation for land sub-division based on location within New Zealand regions (e.g. Wellington region). Shows what is feasible to subdivide based on section area, building footprint, council zoning and district plan rules. https://2017.hackerspace.govhack.org/project/simplocation

Before Feasibility filter applied

After feasiblity filter applied

Datasources:

  • HERE MAPs API for base map (hybrid day)
  • HERE MAPs API for base map (normal day)
  • LINZ Parcels
  • Wellington City Council (zoning map)
  • Wellington City Council (building footprints)
  • Wellington City council district plan rules

Background

THERE IS NO MAGIC BULLET THAT WILL SOLVE THE HOUSING CRISIS.

Housing supply needs to increase so that more people can own a home for the first time.

Simplocation is useful for:

Existing homeowners - people with mortgages; Property buyers and developers; and Professionals
